{
  "stem": "6736.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "They need for the war machine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But, uh, not only-- but to us, we were not hanged up on the material things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "As long as they left us alone, we, we will be satisfied.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "In beginning of 1940, we were told that the large families have to move out from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They asked us to register, my father, my mother, my older brother, myself, and a younger brother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "He was then 12 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "The other ones, they didn't have to register.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And voluntarily, as I have told you before, my father had a brother in Ozarow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "So he went-- they say there's more food in a smaller town-- to leave for Ozarow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "But we didn't want to leave the apartment with all our belongings we couldn't take along with us, so I stayed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I stayed to watch the apartment, so people would not go in and rob the apartment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "There was another few boys from another apartment that they stayed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we stayed together for a few months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then it quieted down a little bit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So while it's quiet down, I wrote my parents they should come back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they came back to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was in the middle  the summer of 1940.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1941, they start talking about making a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But to go into the ghetto, you had to have a small family, and you also had to have papers that you work for the German machinery, German Wehrmacht, or something, that you worked that the Germans have a use from it.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Otherwise, you're going to be deported.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And maybe the end of February or the first week of March in 1941, we sustain ourselves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had some material, because money was no good at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had shoes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had pieces of goods.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
